OL,3,CHead coach Bellamy celebrates first
OL,4,CCymru win in 'toughest conditions'
OL,6,FCraig Bellamy has expressed his pride
OL,7,Fover Wales' win in Montenegro after
OL,8,Ffacing what he said were the toughest
OL,9,Fconditions in his career.
OL,11,FWales claimed their first win under
OL,12,FBellamy with a 2-1 Nations League
OL,13,Fsuccess over Montenegro.
OL,15,FDespite the torrential rain, which saw
OL,16,Fplayers loose their footing and skid
OL,17,Fall over the City Stadium pitch in
OL,18,FNiksic, the Cymru side were off to a
OL,19,Fdream start.
