OL,3,CHead coach Bellamy celebrates first
OL,4,CCymru win in 'toughest conditions'
OL,6,FKieffer Moore and Harry Wilson scored
OL,7,Ftwo goals in the opening three minutes.
OL,9,FMoore's opener was timed at 37 seconds
OL,10,F` Wales' fastest goal since 2003 ` and
OL,11,Fended their longest scoreless streak
OL,12,Fof four games since September 2012.
OL,14,FFollowing the victory, Bellamy: "These
OL,15,Fare the toughest conditions I've been
OL,16,Fin"
OL,18,FHe started his reign with a goalless
OL,19,Fhome draw against Euro 2024 quarter-
OL,20,Ffinalists Turkey on Friday.
