OL,3,CHead coach Bellamy celebrates first
OL,4,CCymru win in 'toughest conditions'
OL,6,F"I'm extremely proud. I love this
OL,7,Fgroup, I really do.
OL,9,F"Nothing about coming here has been
OL,10,Feasy, you could have had a lot of
OL,11,Fexcuses about this trip."
OL,13,FHe continued: "The change of venue
OL,14,F(from Podgorica to Niksic at the end
OL,15,Fof last month), the travel here, a bus
OL,16,Fdriver who took his time, the
OL,17,Fconditions... but sometimes you learn
OL,18,Ffrom it.
