OL,3,CHead coach Bellamy celebrates first
OL,4,CCymru win in 'toughest conditions'
OL,6,F"There is a reason why this group have
OL,7,Fqualified for major tournaments. It
OL,8,Fwasn't a football match. The
OL,9,Fconditions weren't going to allow it.
OL,11,F"Who will win the battle? Who will win
OL,12,Fsecond balls? That's what it turned
OL,13,Fout to be."
OL,15,FHe added: "I take a lot of
OL,16,Fsatisfaction as you show another side.
OL,17,FThis was not part of our plan.
OL,19,F"We saw after five minutes the pitch
OL,20,Ftore up and then it becomes about who
OL,21,Fcan win the battle.
