OL,3,CHead coach Bellamy celebrates first
OL,4,CCymru win in 'toughest conditions'
OL,6,F"It was close at times. It was a
OL,7,Fboxing match. There were two teams on
OL,8,Ftheir feet and we came out on top.
OL,9,FSometimes you take more pride from
OL,10,Fthese wins."
OL,12,FWales' next Nations League test is in
OL,13,FIceland ` beaten 3-1 away by Turkey on
OL,14,FMonday ` on October 11, before the
OL,15,Freturn game against Montenegro at
OL,16,FCardiff City Stadium three days later.
